{
  "stem": "11144.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But who know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From there, we went to a little town named Ludwipol.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's spelled L-U-D-W-I-P-O-L.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And was it east?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "West?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was east.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "East.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was east.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were going east.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was east.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We might have been in some little towns all along the way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I really cannot recall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that I used to be in orphanages-- not, maybe not orphanages, but in like daycare center.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember laying on a cot in the afternoon and sleeping.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, well, I'm going to write a book one day, if I survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But everything just-- I, I, I can't recall these days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I just remember very slight moments and whatever, but not the whole story.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyhow, we went to Ludwipol, Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Again, it was a little town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father got a job there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My uncle caught up with us-- another uncle caught up with us, my mother's, well, still younger brother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother was the oldest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was really the-- he was in, in the fur business with my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he started really selling business, and do some selling and going from town to town and trying to make some living.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father got a job there, again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I went to school there, again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I really had, like, two years of Russian schooling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember, it was my birthday on the 19th of June.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my mother made me a big birthday party.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I had a lot of Ukrainian friends, some Polish friends, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because by then, life had changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the next day, I woke up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And everybody started saying the war, the war broke out 20th of June, 1941.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
